# Phase 1 Audit + Docker Strategy — Self-Deploy Champion Council

---

## Phase 1 Audit Verdict: **PASS — with 6 minor findings**

I read every single file line-by-line. The implementation is **remarkably solid** — clean OOP, proper dependency injection, correct extraction of every critical subsystem I identified in the first evaluation.

